oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bill Monroe at Grundy Jr. High (19429)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Monroe, Bill, 1911-1996; Osborne Brothers; Monroe, James; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color half sheet (red and black on white) announcing Bill Monroe and the Bluegrass Boys, the Osborne Brothers, and James Monroe at the Grundy Jr. High School on February 4. Poster features metal photoplates of Bill Monroe, the Osborne Brothers and James Monroe. To view the paperwork associated with this poster, see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/21025.
